t_photo_series_place::clip_card_2::goals: Akkaataa qopheessaa bakka biraadhaan irra deebi'i.
t_photo_series_place::text_card_1::text: Haala hordoftooti wajjin adda baasan barbaadi.
t_photo_series_place::text_card_0::text: Kun qajoojii walitti fufiinsa bakkaati. Walitti fufiinsi tuuta fakkiiwwan wal fakkaatanii kan qabxii wal dorgomsiisaa ibsaniitii. Fakkiiwwan walitti fufiinsa keessaa caalmaatt wal dorgomsiisuuf haala qophiitiin wal fakkachu qabu.
t_photo_series_place::clip_card_1::goals: Qopheessa suuraa jalqabaa bakka biraadhaan irra deebi'i.
t_photo_series_place::title: Walitti Fufiinsa - Bakka
t_photo_series_place::clip_card_0::goals: Suuraa bakka seenaakeef barbaachisaa ta'ee kaasi.
